				<wikidot:authorName>Zyn</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1404533</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm not sure it's really necessary, given that people check Most Recently Created for new things that they haven't read.</p> <p>Staff might look at this page from time to time (since Series I articles are rarely edited, so if one shows up here, it might merit investigating) but the Recent Changes page tends to be more useful for that sort of thing.</p> <p>If someone would like to voice an opinion about why this page deserves an update, please do so.</p> 
				 	]]>
